噜、咕唧、噗、滋］等拟声词，来模拟唾液交换、吞吐和吸允的声音，例如，啾噜/啾噗代表舌头交缠和噗噜/咕噜代表吞吐含吮）\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();var a=document.querySelector('.chat .chat-bottom .uni-textarea .chat-input-scope textarea');if(a){a.value+=this.dataset.value+'\\n';a.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'))};var p=this.closest('#teapot-draggable-container-1721558234000');if(p){p.querySelector('div:last-child').style.display='none';}\">母猪特化</div>\n    <div style=\"padding: 8px 12px; background-color: rgba(0, 196, 204, 0.85); border: 1px solid #99FFFF; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; color: #99FFFF; backdrop-filter: blur(5px);\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();document.getElementById('teapot-modal-1721558234000').style.display='block';var p=this.closest('#teapot-draggable-container-1721558234000');if(p){p.querySelector('div:last-child').style.display='none';}\">详细说明</div>\n    <div style=\"padding: 8px 12px; background-color: rgba(255, 50, 50, 0.85); border: 1px solid #FF0000; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; color: #FFFFFF; backdrop-filter: blur(5px);\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();var el=this.closest('#teapot-draggable-container-1721558234000');if(el){el.remove();};var modal=document.getElementById('teapot-modal-1721558234000');if(modal){modal.remove();};\">清除悬浮球</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"teapot-modal-1721558234000\" style=\"display: none; position: fixed; left: 50%; top: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); width: 80%; max-width: 500px; max-height: 70%; overflow-y: auto; background-color: rgba(10, 25, 47, 0.95); border: 1px solid #00C4CC; border-radius: 10px; color: #99FFFF; padding: 20px; z-index: 100000; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 196, 204, 0.5); backdrop-filter: blur(8px);\">\n  <h3 style=\"margin-top:0; border-bottom: 1px solid #0077B6; padding-bottom: 10px;\">详细说明</h3>\n  <b>什么模型好用？</b>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">首推：逆向Claude4.5或3.7或4.0，默认token高，搭配指令后，字数多且体验极佳，同时稳定不掉状态栏<br>次推：gemini-2.5-pro。文风好、智商高、模型稳定，但容易绝望神化与繁体字等，也偶尔改变状态栏正则匹配，导致状态栏美化丢失</p>\n  <b>如何