o-intro{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.9);color:#F5ED7A;padding:20px;box-sizing:border-box;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.3s;overflow-y:auto;font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;}\n.teapot-photo-box:hover .teapot-photo-intro{opacity:1;}\n.teapot-nav-row{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;gap:20px;}\n.teapot-arrow-btn{width:45px;height:45px;background:rgba(30,30,50,0.7);border:2px solid #4e4e85;border-radius:8px;color:#F5ED7A;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);}\n.teapot-arrow-btn:hover{background:rgba(106,90,205,0.6);}\n.teapot-page-num{color:#F5ED7A;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;min-width:50px;text-align:center;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"teapot-modal-trigger\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();document.getElementById('teapot_modal_1738284192847').style.display='flex';\">角色图鉴</div>\n<div id=\"teapot_modal_1738284192847\" class=\"teapot-modal-overlay\" onclick=\"if(event.target===this){this.style.display='none';}\">\n<div class=\"teapot-modal-box\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();\">\n<div class=\"teapot-modal-header\">\n<div class=\"teapot-modal-title\">角色展示</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-modal-close\" onclick=\"document.getElementById('teapot_modal_1738284192847').style.display='none';\">×</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-area\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-page active\" data-page=\"1\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-box\">\n<img src=\"https://meimoaiimg.com/user/1355928/illust_130929173_20260217_205220.png\" alt=\"角色1\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-name\">夏川莉子</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-intro\">早熟大胆，小恶魔，爱捉弄人。父亲是渔船船长，从小跟船出海。熟悉海岛秘密小道。\n夏川家:青蓝渔港码头</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-page\" data-page=\"2\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-box\">\n<img src=\"https://meimoaiimg.com/user/1355928/illust_130929173_20260217_205218.png\" alt=\"角色2\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-name\">黑羽夜子</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-intro\">外表高冷孤僻，内心敏感脆弱，不善表达。岛上旧家族后裔，父母常年在本土工作，独自跟奶奶生活。黑羽家:海边复古洋楼。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-page\" data-page=\"3\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-box\">\n<img src=\"https://meimoaiimg.com/user/1355928/illust_130929173_20260217_205222.png\" alt=\"角色3\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-name\">田中阳菜</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-intro\">活泼冒失，热血仗义，孩子王性格。家里开岛上唯一运动用品店，擅长跑步与沙滩运动，学校体育部成员。田中家:海岛运动屋「阳菜Sports」</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-page\" data-page=\"4\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-box\">\n<img src=\"https://meimoaiimg.com/user/1355928/illust_130929173_20260217_205224.png\" alt=\"角色4\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-name\">星野凛</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-intro\">外表叛逆傲娇，内心易害羞紧张。妈妈是岛上美发店老板，自己偷偷学做发型与穿搭，喜欢小众朋克风格。\n星野家:潮色美发沙龙</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-page\" data-page=\"5\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-box\">\n<img src=\"https://meimoaiimg.com/user/1355928/illust_130929173_20260217_205227.png\" alt=\"角色5\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-name\">宫本海夏</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-intro\">开朗外向，热情像小太阳，爱拍照爱交友。家里经营海岛观光摄影店，从小擅长拍照与记录生活。宫本家:海夏写真馆</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-page\" data-page=\"6\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-box\">\n<img src=\"https://meimoaiimg.com/user/1355928/illust_130929173_20260217_205229.png\" alt=\"角色6\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-name\">樱井眠</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-intro\">软萌嗜睡，说话黏人爱撒娇。家里经营岛上老牌民宿，从小习惯在民宿角落睡觉。\n樱井家:青蓝老牌民宿「樱之眠」。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-page\" data-page=\"7\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-box\">\n<img src=\"https://meimoaiimg.com/user/1355928/illust_130929173_20260217_205232.png\" alt=\"角色7\">\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-name\">白川堇</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-photo-intro\">内向害羞，认真固执，笨拙真诚。父亲是岛上小学老师，擅长手工与整理。\n白川家:青蓝岛立小学校附近一户建</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-nav-row\">\n<div class=\"teapot-arrow-btn\" onclick=\"(function(){var modal=document.getElementById('teapot_modal_1738284192847');var current=modal.querySelector('.teapot-photo-page.active');var currentNum=parseInt(current.getAttribute('data-page'));var prevNum=currentNum===1?7:currentNum-1;current.classList.remove('active');modal.querySelector('.teapot-photo-page[data-page=\\''+prevNum+'\\']').classList.add('active');modal.querySelector('.teapot-page-num').textContent=prevNum+'/7';})()\">◀</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-page-num\">1/7</div>\n<div class=\"teapot-arrow-btn\" onclick=\"(function(){var modal=document.getElementById('teapot_modal_1738284192847');var current=modal.querySelector('.teapot-photo-page.active');var currentNum=parseInt(current.getAttribute('data-page'));var nextNum=currentNum===7?1:currentNum+1;current.classList.remove('active');modal.querySelector('.teapot-photo-page[data-page=\\''+nextNum+'\\']').classList.add('active');modal.querySelector('.teapot-page-num').textContent=nextNum+'/7';})()\">▶</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
